| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-3089 — Recovery Inhibition (moneymessage)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 90ec48c5-5f67-5e9b-954d-8ffdb8a408b1"
